burlap.mdp.stochasticgames

Class JointAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.mdp.stochasticgames.JointAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action, Iterable<Action>

    public class JointAction
extends Object
implements Action, Iterable<Action>
    This class specifies which action each agent took in a world, where agents are identified by their player number; that is, the order of the actions determines who selected what.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
